    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>身临其境的潜行与战略要素。<br></li><li>超过15个地点可供盗窃。<br></li><li>敌对角色会对玩家的行为产生真实的反应。<br></li><li>数十种不同的工具和有用的道具。<br></li><li>类似RPG游戏的角色成长系统。<br></li><li>循序渐进的反乌托邦故事剧情。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实施完美盗窃</h2>为盗窃做准备——与线人交谈，选择最合适的工具，使用技能和特长。夜幕降临时，就可以实施盗窃。明智地规划你的行动，寻找正确的方法渗透巧妙的安全系统。但是要小心——这座城市会对你的所有行为做出积极反应，不会原谅任何错误。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/dbc7c7cf1977b1b876ddb73edef5bdce.poster.avif?t=1752001542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/dbc7c7cf1977b1b876ddb73edef5bdce.webm?t=1752001542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/dbc7c7cf1977b1b876ddb73edef5bdce.mp4?t=1752001542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典的反乌托邦</h2>20世纪中期的虚构欧洲。没人能比小偷更好地窥视这个邪恶社会的秘密。探索城市街道，寻找密室，偷听他人对话。每栋房屋和每一个角落都有揭示剧情的讽刺和黑色幽默。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/ec1136866cba1aa0b1b6e19905240f6c.poster.avif?t=1752001542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/ec1136866cba1aa0b1b6e19905240f6c.webm?t=1752001542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/ec1136866cba1aa0b1b6e19905240f6c.mp4?t=1752001542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >学习技能</h2>选择你的游戏风格——你的角色技能成长只取决于你的行动。解锁超过50个技能和特长（特别是足以改变游戏玩法的技能），从普通的街头扒手成长为真正的大师盗贼。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/a5fcc28a08e610f45b10b18ee4994d69.poster.avif?t=1752001542\" width=400 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/a5fcc28a08e610f45b10b18ee4994d69.webm?t=1752001542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803600/extras/a5fcc28a08e610f45b10b18ee4994d69.mp4?t=1752001542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
